ASSET_DSC: FMDR base type - base type for other base types, as well as itself.  It has the base resources for the FMDR as well, XSD libraries, Master Metadata (the doc that services start with).
FURTHeR Logical Model.  Currently a work in progress.
This is the FURTHeR Namespace.  Its metadata are contained in its resources.
The namespace type for the FMDR.  All namespaces declared in the FMDR should be of this type.
Data Set ID is equivalent to an End User's Query ID. It is used to support Queries within another Query Result Set.

A Dummy Attribute Used as a placeholder to associate Source Attributes to Nothing. Then we can create association properties to direct the Query Translation Actions in the XQuery Program. For example, the FURTHER valueType attribute associates to nothing in the OMOPv2 model. Therefore we can associate the valueType to this devNull and assign it association properties to skip this attribute from Query Translation.
